OL,3,CBritney Spears checks herself into
OL,4,Ctreatment facility after DUI arrest
OL,6,FBritney Spears has checked into a
OL,7,Ftreatment facility following her
OL,8,Farrest on suspicion of operating her
OL,9,Fvehicle under the influence last month.
OL,11,FThe Toxic singer was arrested in
OL,12,FCalifornia on March 5 after she was
OL,13,Fseen driving "erratically".
OL,15,FPolice said Spears "showed signs of
OL,16,Fimpairment and submitted to a series
OL,17,Fof field sobriety tests" after being
OL,18,Fpulled over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
