OL,3,CBritney Spears checks herself into
OL,4,Ctreatment facility after DUI arrest
OL,6,FA representative for the singer
OL,7,Fconfirmed she voluntarily checked
OL,8,Fherself into the treatment facility.
OL,10,FSpears, who police said was alone in
OL,11,Fher black BMW 430i, was arrested for
OL,12,F"driving under the influence of a
OL,13,Fcombination of drugs and alcohol" and
OL,14,Ftaken to Ventura County Main Jail,
OL,15,Fnorth west of Los Angeles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
