OL,3,CBritney Spears checks herself into
OL,4,Ctreatment facility after DUI arrest
OL,6,FA representative at the time said the
OL,7,F"unfortunate incident" was "completely
OL,8,Finexcusable", adding it would ideally
OL,9,Fbe "the first step in long overdue
OL,10,Fchange that needs to occur in
OL,11,FBritney's life".
