OL,3,CBritney Spears checks herself into
OL,4,Ctreatment facility after DUI arrest
OL,6,F"Her loved ones are going to come up
OL,7,Fwith an overdue needed plan to set her
OL,8,Fup for success for wellbeing."
OL,10,FVentura County District Attorney's
OL,11,FOffice will make a decision on charges
OL,12,Fagainst Spears before she is due in
OL,13,Fcourt on May 4.
