OL,3,CBritney Spears checks herself into
OL,4,Ctreatment facility after DUI arrest
OL,6,FIn 2007, the Mississippi-born singer
OL,7,Favoided a criminal hit-and-run trial
OL,8,Fby paying for damages after
OL,9,Fphotographers pictured Spears steering
OL,10,Fher car into another vehicle as she
OL,11,Ftried to park in a California car
OL,12,Fpark, and walking away after assessing
OL,13,Fthe damage to her own car.
OL,15,FHer arrest comes after she sold part
OL,16,Fof her rights to her back catalogue in
OL,17,FFebruary to music publisher Primary
OL,18,FWave for an unknown fee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
